        "text": ").",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Are not all these which speak Galilæans?—This was, of course, antecedently probable, but it is singular that this is the first assertion of the fact as regards the whole company. The traitor had been apparently the only exception (see Note on Matthew 10:4), and he had gone to his own place.",
